<span class="postbody">In no paticular order:
<br />

<br />
1) Illusions....make them more viable in groups not just something "fun" or a shrink.  I would also undo the faction nerf.  Include Deception.
<br />

<br />
2) Procs...Give us proc spells or help us increase the DPS of our groups.
<br />

